---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="承認ワークフロー（デモ）| Optiens"
  description="申請者と承認者の画面を切り替えられる、社内承認ワークフローのデモ。経費精算・休暇申請・稟議など、Salesforce 型の承認フローを御社専用に構築できます。"
  canonical="https://optiens.com/approval-workflow"
>
  <main class="aw-main light-section">
    <section class="aw-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="aw-title">承認ワークフロー</h1>
        <p class="aw-lede">
          申請者と承認者で<strong>画面・できる操作が切り替わる</strong>のが、業務システム型ワークフローの基本です。<br class="pc-only">
          このデモではビュー切替で両方の体験を確認できます。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="aw-section">
      <div class="container">

        <!-- ビュー切替 -->
        <div class="view-switch" role="tablist" aria-label="ビュー切替">
          <button type="button" class="view-btn is-active" data-view="submitter" role="tab" aria-selected="true">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-pen"></i>
            <span class="view-btn-name">申請者ビュー</span>
            <span class="view-btn-sub">スタッフ・部長など</span>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="view-btn" data-view="approver" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i>
            <span class="view-btn-name">承認者ビュー</span>
            <span class="view-btn-sub">役員・経営者</span>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="view-reset" id="reset-btn" title="サンプルデータに戻す">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-left"></i> リセット
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- 申請者ビュー -->
        <div class="view-panel" data-view-panel="submitter">
          <div class="aw-grid">
            <!-- 左: 新規申請フォーム -->
            <div class="aw-card">
              <h2 class="aw-card-title">新規申請</h2>
              <form id="submit-form" class="submit-form">
                <label>
                  <span>申請種類</span>
                  <select name="type" required>
                    <option value="expense">経費精算</option>
                    <option value="leave">休暇申請</option>
                    <option value="proposal">稟議書</option>
                    <option value="purchase">発注承認</option>
                    <option value="other">その他</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                <label>
                  <span>件名</span>
                  <input type="text" name="title" required maxlength="60" placeholder="例: 出張旅費精算（5/3 大阪）" />
                </label>
                <label>
                  <span>金額（任意）</span>
                  <input type="number" name="amount" min="0" step="1" placeholder="例: 28500" />
                </label>
                <label>
                  <span>内容・理由</span>
                  <textarea name="body" rows="4" maxlength="500" placeholder="承認に必要な背景・理由を簡潔に記載"></textarea>
                </label>
                <label>
                  <span>承認者</span>
                  <select name="approver" required>
                    <option value="ceo">代表取締役（最終承認）</option>
                    <option value="cfo">CFO（経理・財務）</option>
                    <option value="coo">COO（業務統括）</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                <button type="submit" class="aw-btn-primary">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i> 承認依頼を提出
                </button>
              </form>
            </div>

            <!-- 右: 自分の申請一覧 -->
            <div class="aw-card">
              <h2 class="aw-card-title">自分の申請一覧</h2>
              <div id="submitter-list" class="req-list">
                <p class="req-empty">まだ申請がありません。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 承認者ビュー -->
        <div class="view-panel" data-view-panel="approver" hidden>
          <div class="aw-card aw-card-full">
            <div class="approver-head">
              <h2 class="aw-card-title">承認待ち（自分宛）</h2>
              <span class="approver-id-pill">承認者: <strong id="approver-label">代表取締役</strong></span>
              <select id="approver-switch" class="approver-switch" aria-label="承認者切替">
                <option value="ceo">代表取締役</option>
                <option value="cfo">CFO（経理・財務）</option>
                <option value="coo">COO（業務統括）</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div id="approver-list" class="req-list">
              <p class="req-empty">承認待ちの申請がありません。</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="aw-card">
            <h2 class="aw-card-title">処理済み（承認・却下）</h2>
            <div id="approver-processed" class="req-list req-list-processed">
              <p class="req-empty">処理済みの申請はまだありません。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 拡張可能性 -->
        <div class="aw-extension">
          <div class="aw-extension-head">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrows-turn-to-dots"></i>
            <h3>御社専用版なら、ここから先まで自動化できます</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="aw-extension-lede">
            このデモは「申請」「承認／却下」「ステータス可視化」までですが、御社専用版では以下まで全自動化できます。
          </p>
          <div class="aw-extension-grid">
            <div class="aw-extension-card">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bell"></i>
              <h4>承認者へ即時通知</h4>
              <p>申請が出されたら、承認者の Slack・メール・LINE に即時通知。スマホからワンタップで承認可能。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="aw-extension-card">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i>
              <h4>会計／人事システムへ自動連携</h4>
              <p>承認後、freee 会計・人事労務 / kintone / スプレッドシート等に自動でレコード追加。二重入力撤廃。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="aw-extension-card">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i>
              <h4>多段承認フロー</h4>
              <p>金額・部署・申請種類で承認ルートを自動切替（5万円未満は部長止め、5万円以上は CFO + CEO 等）。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="aw-extension-card">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i>
              <h4>AI 自動レビュー</h4>
              <p>申請内容を AI が事前チェックし、過去類似案件・規定との整合性・記載漏れを承認者に提示。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 注記 -->
        <div class="aw-footnote">
          <p><strong>このデモについて</strong>: 申請データはお使いのブラウザに保存されます（サーバーには送信されません）。「リセット」ボタンでサンプル状態に戻せます。</p>
          <p><strong>弊社での運用</strong>: Optiens 社内では稟議・経費・発注の承認を Supabase + AI 駆動 UI で自動化しています。御社の業務に合わせたカスタム版をご相談いただけます。</p>
          <a href="/ai-examples#case-approval" class="aw-back">← AI活用事例集に戻る</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
type ApprovalRequest = {
  id: string
  type: 'expense' | 'leave' | 'proposal' | 'purchase' | 'other'
  title: string
  amount?: number
  body: string
  submitter: string
  approver: 'ceo' | 'cfo' | 'coo'
  status: 'pending' | 'approved' | 'rejected'
  comment?: string
  createdAt: number
  decidedAt?: number
}

const STORAGE_KEY = 'optiens.approval.demo.v1'
const DEFAULT_SUBMITTER = '田中 一郎（営業部）'

const TYPE_LABELS: Record<ApprovalRequest['type'], string> = {
  expense: '経費精算',
  leave: '休暇申請',
  proposal: '稟議書',
  purchase: '発注承認',
  other: 'その他',
}
const APPROVER_LABELS: Record<ApprovalRequest['approver'], string> = {
  ceo: '代表取締役',
  cfo: 'CFO（経理・財務）',
  coo: 'COO（業務統括）',
}

const SAMPLE: ApprovalRequest[] = [
  {
    id: 'REQ-1001',
    type: 'expense',
    title: '出張旅費精算（5/3 大阪商談）',
    amount: 28500,
    body: '大阪エリアの新規パートナーとの商談に関する旅費精算です。新幹線往復・宿泊・先方手土産。',
    submitter: '田中 一郎（営業部）',
    approver: 'cfo',
    status: 'pending',
    createdAt: Date.now() - 2 * 60 * 60 * 1000,
  },
  {
    id: 'REQ-1002',
    type: 'purchase',
    title: 'GPU PC 購入（ローカル LLM 検証用）',
    amount: 380000,
    body: 'ローカル LLM 運用検証のため RTX 4090 搭載 PC を 1 台購入。社内 AI 自動化の機密データ対応の検証目的。',
    submitter: '佐藤 花子（開発部）',
    approver: 'ceo',
    status: 'pending',
    createdAt: Date.now() - 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000,
  },
  {
    id: 'REQ-1003',
    type: 'leave',
    title: '夏季休暇取得申請（8/12〜8/16）',
    body: '夏季長期休暇 5 営業日の取得申請。引継ぎ事項は別添の通り。',
    submitter: '田中 一郎（営業部）',
    approver: 'coo',
    status: 'approved',
    comment: '了解です。よい休暇を。',
    createdAt: Date.now() - 5 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000,
    decidedAt: Date.now() - 4 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000,
  },
  {
    id: 'REQ-1004',
    type: 'proposal',
    title: '広告予算追加（Q2 リスティング）',
    amount: 250000,
    body: 'Q2 のリスティング広告予算を追加。費用対効果の試算は別添。',
    submitter: '田中 一郎（営業部）',
    approver: 'ceo',
    status: 'rejected',
    comment: '今期は新サービス LP 整備を優先したい。来期再検討。',
    createdAt: Date.now() - 10 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000,
    decidedAt: Date.now() - 9 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000,
  },
]

function loadRequests(): ApprovalRequest[] {
  try {
    const raw = localStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY)
    if (raw) return JSON.parse(raw) as ApprovalRequest[]
  } catch {}
  return [...SAMPLE]
}
function saveRequests(items: ApprovalRequest[]) {
  localStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(items))
}

let requests = loadRequests()

function fmtAmount(n?: number) {
  if (n == null || n === 0) return ''
  return '¥' + n.toLocaleString('ja-JP')
}
function fmtRelative(ms: number) {
  const diff = Date.now() - ms
  const min = Math.floor(diff / 60000)
  if (min < 1) return 'たった今'
  if (min < 60) return `${min} 分前`
  const hr = Math.floor(min / 60)
  if (hr < 24) return `${hr} 時間前`
  const day = Math.floor(hr / 24)
  return `${day} 日前`
}
function statusBadge(s: ApprovalRequest['status']) {
  if (s === 'pending') return '<span class="status-pill status-pending">承認待ち</span>'
  if (s === 'approved') return '<span class="status-pill status-approved">承認済</span>'
  return '<span class="status-pill status-rejected">却下</span>'
}
function escapeHtml(s: string) {
  return s.replace(/[&<>"']/g, c => ({ '&': '&amp;', '<': '&lt;', '>': '&gt;', '"': '&quot;', "'": '&#39;' }[c] as string))
}

function reqCard(r: ApprovalRequest, mode: 'submitter' | 'approver-pending' | 'approver-processed') {
  const amt = fmtAmount(r.amount)
  const decisionInfo = (r.status !== 'pending' && r.decidedAt)
    ? `<div class="req-decision">${statusBadge(r.status)} <span class="req-decision-meta">${fmtRelative(r.decidedAt)}</span>${r.comment ? `<p class="req-comment">${escapeHtml(r.comment)}</p>` : ''}</div>`
    : ''

  const actions = mode === 'approver-pending'
    ? `<div class="req-actions">
         <button class="req-btn req-btn-approve" data-approve="${r.id}"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> 承認</button>
         <button class="req-btn req-btn-reject" data-reject="${r.id}"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i> 却下</button>
       </div>`
    : ''

  return `
    <article class="req-item req-${r.status}">
      <header class="req-head">
        <span class="req-id">${r.id}</span>
        <span class="req-type">${TYPE_LABELS[r.type]}</span>
        ${mode === 'submitter' ? statusBadge(r.status) : ''}
        <time class="req-time">${fmtRelative(r.createdAt)}</time>
      </header>
      <h3 class="req-title">${escapeHtml(r.title)}${amt ? ` <span class="req-amount">${amt}</span>` : ''}</h3>
      <div class="req-meta">
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i> 申請者: ${escapeHtml(r.submitter)}</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i> 承認者: ${APPROVER_LABELS[r.approver]}</span>
      </div>
      ${r.body ? `<p class="req-body">${escapeHtml(r.body)}</p>` : ''}
      ${decisionInfo}
      ${actions}
    </article>
  `
}

// ===== レンダー =====
function renderSubmitter() {
  const list = document.getElementById('submitter-list')!
  const own = requests.filter(r => r.submitter === DEFAULT_SUBMITTER).sort((a, b) => b.createdAt - a.createdAt)
  if (own.length === 0) {
    list.innerHTML = '<p class="req-empty">まだ申請がありません。</p>'
    return
  }
  list.innerHTML = own.map(r => reqCard(r, 'submitter')).join('')
}

let currentApprover: ApprovalRequest['approver'] = 'ceo'
function renderApprover() {
  const pendingList = document.getElementById('approver-list')!
  const processedList = document.getElementById('approver-processed')!
  const pending = requests.filter(r => r.approver === currentApprover && r.status === 'pending').sort((a, b) => b.createdAt - a.createdAt)
  const processed = requests.filter(r => r.approver === currentApprover && r.status !== 'pending').sort((a, b) => (b.decidedAt || 0) - (a.decidedAt || 0))

  pendingList.innerHTML = pending.length === 0
    ? '<p class="req-empty">承認待ちの申請がありません。</p>'
    : pending.map(r => reqCard(r, 'approver-pending')).join('')

  processedList.innerHTML = processed.length === 0
    ? '<p class="req-empty">処理済みの申請はまだありません。</p>'
    : processed.map(r => reqCard(r, 'approver-processed')).join('')

  document.getElementById('approver-label')!.textContent = APPROVER_LABELS[currentApprover]
}

function rerender() {
  renderSubmitter()
  renderApprover()
}

// ===== ビュー切替 =====
document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.view-btn').forEach((btn) => {
  btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const view = btn.getAttribute('data-view')!
    document.querySelectorAll('.view-btn').forEach(b => {
      b.classList.toggle('is-active', b === btn)
      b.setAttribute('aria-selected', b === btn ? 'true' : 'false')
    })
    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.view-panel').forEach(p => {
      p.hidden = p.getAttribute('data-view-panel') !== view
    })
  })
})

// ===== 申請フォーム =====
const form = document.getElementById('submit-form') as HTMLFormElement
form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
  e.preventDefault()
  const fd = new FormData(form)
  const newId = 'REQ-' + Math.floor(1000 + Math.random() * 9000)
  const amount = Number(fd.get('amount') || 0)
  const newReq: ApprovalRequest = {
    id: newId,
    type: fd.get('type') as ApprovalRequest['type'],
    title: String(fd.get('title') || '').slice(0, 60),
    amount: amount > 0 ? amount : undefined,
    body: String(fd.get('body') || '').slice(0, 500),
    submitter: DEFAULT_SUBMITTER,
    approver: fd.get('approver') as ApprovalRequest['approver'],
    status: 'pending',
    createdAt: Date.now(),
  }
  requests = [newReq, ...requests]
  saveRequests(requests)
  form.reset()
  rerender()
})

// ===== 承認・却下 =====
document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
  const target = e.target as HTMLElement
  const approveBtn = target.closest<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-approve]')
  const rejectBtn = target.closest<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-reject]')
  if (approveBtn) {
    const id = approveBtn.getAttribute('data-approve')!
    const r = requests.find(x => x.id === id)
    if (!r) return
    const c = window.prompt('承認コメント（任意）', '承認します。')
    r.status = 'approved'
    r.decidedAt = Date.now()
    if (c) r.comment = c
    saveRequests(requests)
    rerender()
  }
  if (rejectBtn) {
    const id = rejectBtn.getAttribute('data-reject')!
    const r = requests.find(x => x.id === id)
    if (!r) return
    const c = window.prompt('却下理由（必須）', '')
    if (!c) return
    r.status = 'rejected'
    r.decidedAt = Date.now()
    r.comment = c
    saveRequests(requests)
    rerender()
  }
})

// ===== 承認者切替 =====
const approverSwitch = document.getElementById('approver-switch') as HTMLSelectElement
approverSwitch.addEventListener('change', () => {
  currentApprover = approverSwitch.value as ApprovalRequest['approver']
  renderApprover()
})

// ===== リセット =====
document.getElementById('reset-btn')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
  if (window.confirm('サンプルデータに戻しますか？（自分の申請内容は消えます）')) {
    requests = [...SAMPLE]
    saveRequests(requests)
    rerender()
  }
})

rerender()
</script>

<style>
  .aw-main {
    background: #F8FAFD;
  }
  .aw-hero {
    padding: clamp(96px, 12vw, 140px) 0 clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.08);
  }
  .aw-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: #6B85C9;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .aw-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.4vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
  }
  .aw-lede {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.4vw, 1rem);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .aw-section {
    padding: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px) 0 clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px);
  }

  /* ビュー切替 */
  .view-switch {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .view-btn {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 2px solid rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .view-btn:hover { border-color: rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.30); }
  .view-btn.is-active {
    border-color: #1F3A93;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.05) 0%, rgba(107, 133, 201, 0.04) 100%);
  }
  .view-btn i {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.10);
    color: #1F3A93;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .view-btn-name {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .view-btn-sub {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .view-reset {
    padding: 8px 14px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.25);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .view-reset:hover { color: #1F3A93; border-color: #1F3A93; }

  /* グリッド */
  .aw-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.3fr);
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .aw-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.10);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .aw-card-full {
    /* approver pending list が幅広 */
  }
  .aw-card-title {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }

  /* フォーム */
  .submit-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .submit-form label {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
  }
  .submit-form label span {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #475569;
  }
  .submit-form input,
  .submit-form select,
  .submit-form textarea {
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.18);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-family: inherit;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .submit-form textarea { resize: vertical; }
